## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-102">将 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 和 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> 对象与和结合使用 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 是设计的语义结构的最简单方法 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-102">Use of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> objects, in conjunction with <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, is the easiest way to design a semantic structure for a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-103">通过获取的实例，通过的属性访问短语的语义信息 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-103">Semantic information for a phrase is accessed by obtaining an instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticValue>, through the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase.Semantics%2A> property on <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.RecognizedPhrase>.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-104">由对象管理的值 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 由 <xref:System.Object> 传递给其构造函数的实例定义。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-104">Values managed by <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> objects are defined by <xref:System.Object> instances passed to their constructors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-105">此的基础类型 <xref:System.Object> 必须是 `bool` 、、 `int` `float` 或 `string` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-105">The underlying type of this <xref:System.Object> must be `bool`, `int`, `float`, or `string`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-106">任何其他类型都将阻止使用构造 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 实例 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-106">Any other type will prevent construction of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> instance with the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-107">实例的典型用法是将 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 实例与的可识别组件（如 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> 短语、规则或对象）相关联 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-107">The typical use of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> instance associates the instance with a recognizable component of a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar>, such as a phrase, a rule, or a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-108">如果将关联的组件用作识别操作的一部分，则将 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 用于定义所返回短语的语义中的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-108">If the associated component is used as part of a recognition operation, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> is used to define a value in the semantics of the returned phrase.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="8a41c-109">有两种将实例与语法元素相关联的基本方法 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> ，具体取决于用于创建的构造函数 <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a41c-109">There are two basic methods for associating a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> instance with a grammar element, depending on the constructor used to create the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>.</span></span>  
  
